---
title: Sarh — Conceptual ERD (Chen-style, high-level entities + relationships)
---
flowchart TB
    %% Sarh brand-coloured Chen-style ERD. Entities are rectangles,
    %% relationships are diamonds, key attributes hang off entities.

    %% ---- Core entities --------------------------------------------------
    Citizen[CITIZEN]
    Officer[OFFICER<br/>registry / reviewer / id_issuer]
    Manager[DEPARTMENT_MANAGER]
    Property[PROPERTY]
    Request[REGISTRATION_REQUEST]
    Document[PROPERTY_DOCUMENT]
    Card[DIGITAL_ID_CARD]
    NFC[NFC_CARD]
    Wallet[SSI_WALLET]
    VC[VERIFIABLE_CREDENTIAL]
    Deed[DEED_PDF]
    QR[VERIFY_QR]
    NFT[PROPERTY_NFT]
    OH[OWNERSHIP_HISTORY]
    Tx[BLOCKCHAIN_TX]
    SC[SMART_CONTRACT]
    Region[REGION]
    Notif[NOTIFICATION]
    Audit[AUDIT_ENTRY]

    %% ---- Relationships (diamonds) --------------------------------------
    R_owns{{owns}}
    R_holds{{holds}}
    R_controls{{controls}}
    R_submits{{submits}}
    R_reviews{{reviews}}
    R_finalapprove{{final approves}}
    R_issues{{issues}}
    R_mints{{triggers mint}}
    R_attaches{{has}}
    R_produces{{produces}}
    R_embeds{{embeds}}
    R_encoded{{encoded as}}
    R_stores{{stores}}
    R_link{{linked to}}
    R_minted{{minted via}}
    R_governs{{governed by}}
    R_chain{{transfer chain}}
    R_scope_c{{scopes}}
    R_scope_p{{scopes}}
    R_scope_o{{scopes}}
    R_recv{{receives}}
    R_audit{{writes}}

    Citizen --- R_owns ---|1..N| Property
    Citizen --- R_holds ---|0..1| Card
    Citizen --- R_controls ---|0..1| Wallet
    Citizen --- R_submits --- Request
    Citizen --- R_recv --- Notif

    Officer --- R_reviews --- Request
    Officer --- R_issues --- Card
    Officer --- R_audit --- Audit

    Manager --- R_finalapprove --- Request
    Manager --- R_mints --- NFT

    Property --- R_attaches --- Document
    Property --- R_produces --- Deed
    Property --- R_chain --- OH
    Property -.->|tokenised as| NFT

    Request --- Property

    Deed --- R_embeds --- QR

    Card --- R_encoded --- NFC
    Card --- Wallet
    Wallet --- R_stores --- VC
    NFT --- R_link --- VC

    NFT --- R_minted --- Tx
    NFT --- R_governs --- SC
    NFT --- OH

    Region --- R_scope_c --- Citizen
    Region --- R_scope_p --- Property
    Region --- R_scope_o --- Officer

    %% ---- Sample attributes (key + identifying) -------------------------
    A_cn((national_id)) --- Citizen
    A_cf((full_name_ar)) --- Citizen
    A_pdid((did)) --- Wallet
    A_pcode((property_code)) --- Property
    A_pstatus((status)) --- Property
    A_token((token_id)) --- NFT
    A_meta((metadata_uri)) --- NFT
    A_ohto((to_did)) --- OH
    A_dno((digital_id_number)) --- Card
    A_nuid((nfc_uid)) --- NFC
    A_qr((verify_url)) --- QR
    A_ttx((tx_hash)) --- Tx
    A_net((network)) --- Tx
    A_role((role)) --- Officer
    A_dept((department)) --- Manager
    A_rcode((code)) --- Region